  "original_title": "\u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Archbishop Condemns Attack on Demonstrators",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo District Archbishop Melcolm Cardinal Ranjith Andagai has issued his strong condemnation of the incident of unarmed civilians being attacked by the police and the military on the unarmed civilians in front of Ranil Wickremesinghe's office within 24 hours of Ranil Wickremesinghe's inauguration.",
        "An independent and transparent inquiry must be conducted into this brutal attack. Furthermore, the Archbishop of Colombo requested the national and international community and the Sarvathe Human Rights Commission to take legal action against all those involved in this attack and said that President Ranil Wickremesinghe should take responsibility for all of them if there are any bad incidents in the future due to this inhumane attack.",
        "He said the above while meeting the media on Friday afternoon at the Colombo Archbishop's residence.",
        "\"I strongly condemn the brutal attacks by the police and the army on the protestors who were unarmed and were carrying out democratic protests without engaging in any kind of violence while sleeping in empty-faced and presidential secretariat front protest fields.",
        "The president must be directly responsible for such repressive actions, bringing international disgrace and pressure to get cooperation to solve the economic crisis.",
        "Some of the young protestors were seriously injured and some were arrested by the police in the attack by the army and police.",
        "Also, I express my complete opposition to the attack on local and foreign journalists there which is a despicable act.",
        "We strongly condemn the inhumane and illegal attack on civilians within 24 hours of Ranil Wickremesinghe's inauguration as President.",
        "Ranil Wickramasinghe, who did not have the mandate of the people, claimed to protect the constitution and became the president only because of the overwhelming votes of the members of parliament.",
        "He has completely violated the fundamental right of freedom of speech and protest given to a citizen of this country as per the constitution. \"While the protestors said that they will remove the tents from the presidential secretariat complex today (yesterday) afternoon, President Ranil Wickremesinghe should be held responsible for the brutal attack and if any future incidents are attributed to this inhumane attack,\" he said."
      ],
